MPD-notify notifies you on MPD's state. It will show a notification on song change and on play/pause/stop. 

To be able to use this, you will need to have the following dependencies:
 1. libnotify
 2. libmpdclient

I have forked the original project by Christian Hesse (mail@eworm.de) and as such, all credit should still be given to him. 
I asked for his permission to upload this and it has been granted.

